*** 20011129_1 by db
- since the old code did a ++addr_count then compared to RES_MAXADDRS,
  it would not find any ip's, depending on the compilers interpretation
  of sequence points. Its quite possible, it would have resolved on sunpro
  compiler, but it sure does not on freebsd gcc.



