*** 20010810_1 by leeh
- wrapped TS5 in #ifdef's
  I need to add doc/ts5.txt later


*** 20010806_2 by leeh
- added a special case exception for juped channels.
  if the channel is juped, and has no users, always use the incoming TS,
  even if its older, else if a channel is juped on a hub, youll get a TS
  desync


*** 20010806_1 by wcampbel
