  if someone squits *us*, use cptr->name, not cptr->host


*** 20010722_2 by db
- Don't show ip's on auto conns



*** 20010722_1 by db
*sigh*
1) NO_HACK_OPS is broken atm, all servers in the network have to
   run this, or servers have to send deops, else you get desyncs.
   I'll look at this some more later.
2) Don't allow opers to gain ops on splits ever (for now, other networks
   might wish to allow this) But allow opers to join channels on splits.



